On this page you can add a new usergroup leader to one of your custom groups.  Select a usergroup below and enter the exact username of the user whom you want to make leader.  Click the "Add" button to continue.<br /><br />

Usergroup leaders can moderate join requests for their group from the <a href="../profile.php?do=editusergroups" target="_blank">Group Memberships</a> section of their User CP.